<P>[What <HI>Silius</HI> writes about the Top of Burning <HI>Aetn<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">.</HI>] Would it not be a most Irksome Thing to have a perpetual <HI>Winter</HI> upon us? But let all <HI>Unregenerates</HI> know, That it is always <HI>winter</HI> with them. Consider Sirs, Consider whether you have no<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter"> the signs of the worst <HI>winter,</HI> in the World upon you. The Cold of the <HI>winter</HI> does make things to become <HI>Un<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">ctive.</HI> As <HI><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"></HI> and the like Instruments will not Go in the <HI>winter;</HI> even the very Moral o<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter"> them sometimes is thereby dis|tended so that their Teeth lose their Congruity; thus the <HI>Owners</HI> are sufficiently Listless too. And are not <HI>you <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">?</HI> You can't <HI>Come,</HI> no, nor so much as <HI>Look,</HI> to the Lord Jesus Christ, for <HI>Life,</HI> tho' the Life of your Souls depend upon it. You can't W<HI>alk</HI> with <HI>G</HI>od, or <HI>Move</HI> with any Activity, much less, can you <HI><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"></HI> with an <HI>Enlarged Heart</HI> in the <HI>Way of His Commandments.</HI> Again, The Cold of
